    "Dataset Features Selected and Importance 4.",
    "Training: Ensemble learns from scratch via a pre-designated training set, expanded to include both the original and artificial ones created using SMOTE.",
    "Iterative construction created the decision trees that yield the RF ensemble.",
    "Each tree is trained using a bootstrap sample, a resampled subset obtained from the enhanced training data.",
